data.description: Beautiful Townhouse in Prestigious Gated Community. Spacious Living-Room and Dining-Room, Large Kitchen w/ Wood Cabinets & Newer S. S Appliances, Brand New Built in Microwave, Brand New Dryer. Laminated Wood Floors throughout home. Master Bedroom upstairs with Walk in Closet, Updated Master Bathroom and Guest Bathroom. Roofed Screened in Patio with Storage Space. Accordion Hurricane Shutters. Spacious Driveway. Cable, Internet & Insurance included in HOA Fees. Pets Ok. Investors Ok. Resort Style Community w/ Pools, Spa, Clubhouses, Playgrounds, Gym, Picnic Area, Basketball, Volleyball, Tennis, Pickleball Courts, Gated Comnty w/ Guards. Great Location, Great Schools!!
